description: AMUNDI PRIME JAPAN UCITS ETF DR seeks to replicate, as closely as possible, the performance of Solactive GBS Japan Large & Mid Cap Index (Net Total return) whether it is rising or falling. This ETF offers exposure to the large and mid-cap companies on the Japanese market. For further information, please also refer to the fund prospectus or www.solactive.com.
name: Amundi Prime Japan UCITS ETF DR (D)
